subject: docs(all): create all maintained documents per CLAUDE.md standards
body:
Created all documents specified in the Documentation section of CLAUDE.md:
- SESSION_NOTES.md: current session context snapshot
- TODO.md: pending work across features, technical, UX, testing
- HISTORY.md: record of completed work
- USER_ACTIONS.md: pending manual actions (Supabase setup, Mapbox token)
- AI_MISTAKES.md: learnings to prevent repeated errors
- USER_GUIDE.md: placeholder user documentation
- TESTING_GUIDE.md: build and database verification steps
- README.md: updated with project overview, setup, and structure

Removed .gitkeep placeholders since directories now have real content.
